      "name": "Upload",
      "description": "**Owned by this service** (requires Bearer token)\n\nSaves a base64-encoded HTML file to local disk and returns a public URL. Used to generate proposal pages.\n\n**Workflow:**\n1. `POST /api/upload/proposal` → get back a `url`\n2. Pass that `url` to `POST /api/leads/:id/proposal` to send the proposal to the client",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Proposal HTML",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fileName\": \"proposal-acme-2026.html\",\n  \"mimeType\": \"text/html\",\n  \"contentBase64\": \"PCFET0NUWVBFIGh0bWw+PGh0bWw+PGJvZHk+PGgxPlByb3Bvc2FsPC9oMT48L2JvZHk+PC9odG1sPg==\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/upload/proposal",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "upload", "proposal"]
            },
            "description": "Saves a base64-encoded HTML string to `uploads/proposals/` and returns a public URL.\n\nThe example `contentBase64` decodes to `<!DOCTYPE html><html><body><h1>Proposal</h1></body></html>`."
          }
        }
